---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout locale="en" title="The platform for high-ticket sales" description="ClosersMatch connects companies with certified closers and appointment setters. In-house training, no cure no pay model, scalable sales system.">

  <!-- ================================================
       HERO
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container hero__inner">

      <!-- LEFT: tekst -->
      <div class="hero__content">
        <p class="hero__eyebrow">ClosersMatch | THE REVENUE ECOSYSTEM</p>

        <h1 class="hero__title">
          Outsource high-ticket sales.<br />
          <span class="hero__title-red">No Cure No Pay.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="hero__subtitle">Warm leads that don't close cost you revenue every day. ClosersMatch matches you with certified closers who take over your sales process. You only pay for results.</p>

        <div class="hero__trust">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          <span>Every closer completes an intensive training program with role-play exercises. Only those who can demonstrably close are admitted.</span>
        </div>

        <div class="hero__actions">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--red btn--lg hero__cta-primary">
            Looking for a closer? Schedule your free intake →
          </a>
          <a href="/for-closers" class="btn btn--outline-dark-mode hero__cta-secondary">
            I'm a setter or closer →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- RIGHT: foto + diagram overlay -->
      <div class="hero__visual">
        <div class="hero__photo-wrap">
          <img
            src="/images/team-hero.png"
            alt="ClosersMatch team of closers and appointment setters"
            class="hero__photo"
            loading="eager"
          />
          <div class="hero__diagram-wrap">
            <img
              src="/images/ecosysteem.png"
              alt="ClosersMatch ecosystem diagram"
              class="hero__diagram"
              loading="eager"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       LOGO STRIP — SECTIE 2
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="logos-strip">
    <h2 class="logos-strip__label">More than 50 successful matches between closers and companies</h2>
    <div class="logos-track-wrap">
      <div class="logos-track" aria-label="Client logos">
        <img src="/images/logos/logo-1.webp" alt="ClosersMatch client" class="logo-img" />
        <img src="/images/logos/logo-2.webp" alt="ClosersMatch client" class="logo-img" />
        <img src="/images/logos/logo-3.webp" alt="ClosersMatch client" class="logo-img" />
        <img src="/images/logos/logo-4.webp" alt="ClosersMatch client" class="logo-img" />
        <img src="/images/logos/logo-5.webp" alt="ClosersMatch client" class="logo-img" />
        <img src="/images/logos/logo-6.webp" alt="ClosersMatch client" class="logo-img" />
        <img src="/images/logos/logo-7.webp" alt="ClosersMatch client" class="logo-img" />
        <img src="/images/logos/logo-8.webp" alt="ClosersMatch client" class="logo-img" />
        <!-- Duplicaat voor naadloze loop -->
        <img src="/images/logos/logo-1.webp" alt="" class="logo-img" aria-hidden="true" />
        <img src="/images/logos/logo-2.webp" alt="" class="logo-img" aria-hidden="true" />
        <img src="/images/logos/logo-3.webp" alt="" class="logo-img" aria-hidden="true" />
        <img src="/images/logos/logo-4.webp" alt="" class="logo-img" aria-hidden="true" />
        <img src="/images/logos/logo-5.webp" alt="" class="logo-img" aria-hidden="true" />
        <img src="/images/logos/logo-6.webp" alt="" class="logo-img" aria-hidden="true" />
        <img src="/images/logos/logo-7.webp" alt="" class="logo-img" aria-hidden="true" />
        <img src="/images/logos/logo-8.webp" alt="" class="logo-img" aria-hidden="true" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       ECOSYSTEEM — SECTIE 3
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="section ecosystem">
    <div class="container">

      <!-- BOVENSTE RIJ: links titel/intro, rechts "anders" + stappen -->
      <div class="ecosystem__top">

        <!-- LINKS: label, titel, probleembeschrijving -->
        <div class="ecosystem__left">
          <span class="label">The commercial ecosystem</span>
          <h2 class="h2 ecosystem__title">From first contact<br />to closed deal.</h2>
          <p class="ecosystem__subkop">Not one link in the chain. The complete commercial ecosystem.</p>
          <p class="ecosystem__body">
            Most companies patch together five separate solutions.<br />
            A setter here. A closer there. A CRM somewhere else.<br />
            Nobody owns the whole process.<br />
            That is exactly where revenue leaks out.
          </p>
          <a href="/workflow" class="btn btn--red btn--lg ecosystem__cta" style="margin-top: 32px; display: inline-flex;">Discover how it works →</a>
        </div>

        <!-- RECHTS: statement + 5 stappen -->
        <div class="ecosystem__right">
          <div class="ecosystem__statement">
            <p class="ecosystem__statement-lead">ClosersMatch is different.</p>
            <p>Five elements. One system. One owner.<br />That is the ClosersMatch commercial ecosystem.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="ecosystem__steps">

            <div class="ecosystem__step">
              <div class="ecosystem__step-icon">
                <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 01-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 01-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 013.07 9.81 19.79 19.79 0 01.06 1.24 2 2 0 012 .06h3a2 2 0 012 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 00.7 2.81 2 2 0 01-.45 2.11L6.09 7.91a16 16 0 006 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 012.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 002.81.7A2 2 0 0122 14.92z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div class="ecosystem__step-body">
                <h3 class="ecosystem__step-title">Qualify</h3>
                <p class="ecosystem__step-text">Setters screen leads. Only serious buyers reach your calendar.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="ecosystem__step">
              <div class="ecosystem__step-icon">
                <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 000-7.78z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div class="ecosystem__step-body">
                <h3 class="ecosystem__step-title">Close</h3>
                <p class="ecosystem__step-text">Certified closers run the conversation. The deal gets closed.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="ecosystem__step">
              <div class="ecosystem__step-icon">
                <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M3 9h18M9 21V9"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div class="ecosystem__step-body">
                <h3 class="ecosystem__step-title">Structure</h3>
                <p class="ecosystem__step-text">Proven sales process, scripts, and CRM setup, ready to use.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="ecosystem__step">
              <div class="ecosystem__step-icon">
                <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div class="ecosystem__step-body">
                <h3 class="ecosystem__step-title">Monitor</h3>
                <p class="ecosystem__step-text">Full visibility into pipeline, calls, and results through the platform.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="ecosystem__step">
              <div class="ecosystem__step-icon">
                <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div class="ecosystem__step-body">
                <h3 class="ecosystem__step-title">Optimize</h3>
                <p class="ecosystem__step-text">Ongoing coaching. Every closer gets better. Every week.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

      </div>


    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       CM CERTIFIED — SECTIE 3
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="section certified">
    <div class="container">

      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="certified__header">
        <span class="label label--red">CM Certified</span>
        <h2 class="h2 certified__title">Not everyone makes it<br />through our selection.</h2>
        <p class="certified__body">
          Every closer and appointment setter in our ecosystem completes an intensive training program.
          Role-play, practical assessments, and industry-specific sales scenarios.
          Those who do not perform are not admitted.
          Those who are admitted are ready to close.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Profielkaarten -->
      <p class="certified__grid-label">A selection from our network.</p>
      <div class="certified__grid">

        <!-- Jeffrey Verhoek -->
        <div class="closer-profile">
          <div class="closer-profile__img-wrap">
            <span class="closer-profile__badge">CM Certified</span>
            <img src="/images/closers/jeffrey-verhoek.png" alt="Jeffrey Verhoek — High Ticket Closer" class="closer-profile__img" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="closer-profile__info">
            <strong class="closer-profile__name">Jeffrey Verhoek</strong>
            <div class="closer-profile__tags">
              <span class="closer-profile__tag">Marketing & Advertising</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Malu Gris -->
        <div class="closer-profile">
          <div class="closer-profile__img-wrap">
            <span class="closer-profile__badge">CM Certified</span>
            <img src="/images/closers/malu-gris.png" alt="Malu Gris — High Ticket Closer" class="closer-profile__img" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="closer-profile__info">
            <strong class="closer-profile__name">Malu Gris</strong>
            <div class="closer-profile__tags">
              <span class="closer-profile__tag">Marketing & Advertising</span>
              <span class="closer-profile__tag">Coaching & Consulting</span>
              <span class="closer-profile__tag closer-profile__tag--more">+3</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Robert van Scherpenzeel -->
        <div class="closer-profile">
          <div class="closer-profile__img-wrap">
            <span class="closer-profile__badge">CM Certified</span>
            <img src="/images/closers/robert-van-scherpenzeel.png" alt="Robert van Scherpenzeel — High Ticket Closer" class="closer-profile__img" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="closer-profile__info">
            <strong class="closer-profile__name">Robert van Scherpenzeel</strong>
            <div class="closer-profile__tags">
              <span class="closer-profile__tag">Coaching & Consulting</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Thomas Bruin -->
        <div class="closer-profile">
          <div class="closer-profile__img-wrap">
            <span class="closer-profile__badge">CM Certified</span>
            <img src="/images/closers/thomas-bruin.png" alt="Thomas Bruin — High Ticket Closer" class="closer-profile__img" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="closer-profile__info">
            <strong class="closer-profile__name">Thomas Bruin</strong>
            <div class="closer-profile__tags">
              <span class="closer-profile__tag">Marketing & Advertising</span>
              <span class="closer-profile__tag">Real Estate</span>
              <span class="closer-profile__tag closer-profile__tag--more">+4</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="certified__cta-wrap">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn--red btn--lg" data-meeting-modal-person="business">View all CM Certified closers →</button>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       HOE HET WERKT — NIEUW (4 STAPPEN)
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="section process">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="process__header">
        <span class="label">How it works</span>
        <h2 class="h2 process__title">From first conversation<br />to closed deal.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="process__grid">

        <!-- Stap 1 -->
        <div class="process__card">
          <div class="process__card-visual">
            <span class="process__step-num">01</span>
            <img src="/images/process/step-1-intake.png" alt="Intake" class="process__card-img" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="process__card-body">
            <h3 class="process__card-title">Intake</h3>
            <p class="process__card-text">We learn your business, product, and target audience. Together we determine which closer or setter profile fits best, by industry, sales style, and deal size.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Stap 2 -->
        <div class="process__card">
          <div class="process__card-visual">
            <span class="process__step-num">02</span>
            <img src="/images/process/step-2-matching.png" alt="Matching" class="process__card-img" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="process__card-body">
            <h3 class="process__card-title">Matching</h3>
            <p class="process__card-text">Within 48 hours we connect you with CM Certified closers and setters from our network. No stacks of résumés. No job interviews. We filter.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Stap 3 -->
        <div class="process__card">
          <div class="process__card-visual">
            <span class="process__step-num">03</span>
            <img src="/images/process/step-3-onboarding.png" alt="Onboarding" class="process__card-img" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="process__card-body">
            <h3 class="process__card-title">Onboarding</h3>
            <p class="process__card-text">Closers are onboarded on your product, market, and customer. Free of charge. That is part of the ecosystem, not an extra service.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Stap 4 -->
        <div class="process__card">
          <div class="process__card-visual">
            <span class="process__step-num">04</span>
            <img src="/images/process/step-4-resultaat.png" alt="Resultaat" class="process__card-img" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="process__card-body">
            <h3 class="process__card-title">Results</h3>
            <p class="process__card-text">The system goes live. Leads are qualified. Conversations happen. Deals get closed. You pay only for results.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="process__cta">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn--red btn--lg" data-meeting-modal-choice>Book your free intake →</button>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       KLANTRESULTATEN — SOCIAL PROOF
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="section results">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="results__header">
        <span class="label">Client results</span>
        <h2 class="h2 results__title">These are not forecasts.<br />These are results.</h2>
        <p class="results__sub">Three companies. Three industries. All with results from week one.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="results__grid">

        <!-- DetachPro -->
        <div class="result-card">
          <div class="result-card__top">
            <div class="result-card__logo-wrap">
              <img src="/images/clients/detachpro.png" alt="DetachPro" class="result-card__logo" />
            </div>
            <p class="result-card__desc">Connects technical professionals with companies.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="result-card__result">
            <span class="result-card__arrow">→</span>
            <span class="result-card__highlight">€50,000 deal closed in week one</span>
          </div>
          <p class="result-card__note">No ramp-up period. Immediate commercial results.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Van de Bilt Energy -->
        <div class="result-card result-card--featured">
          <div class="result-card__top">
            <div class="result-card__logo-wrap result-card__logo-wrap--dark">
              <img src="/images/clients/van-de-bilt-energy.png" alt="Van de Bilt Energy" class="result-card__logo" />
            </div>
            <p class="result-card__desc">Supplier of home battery systems and sustainable energy solutions.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="result-card__result">
            <span class="result-card__arrow">→</span>
            <span class="result-card__highlight">Two systems sold in week one</span>
          </div>
          <p class="result-card__note">From lead to closed deal. Fast conversion, proven proposition.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Leadstars -->
        <div class="result-card">
          <div class="result-card__top">
            <div class="result-card__logo-wrap result-card__logo-wrap--dark">
              <img src="/images/clients/leadstars.png" alt="Leadstars" class="result-card__logo" />
            </div>
            <p class="result-card__desc">Helps companies grow structurally through visibility, leads, and deals.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="result-card__result">
            <span class="result-card__arrow">→</span>
            <span class="result-card__highlight">€20,000+ per month in new deals</span>
          </div>
          <p class="result-card__note">Consistent deal flow. Scalable and measurable.</p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="results__cta">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn--red btn--lg" data-meeting-modal-choice>Plan your success now →</button>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================================
       NO CURE NO PAY — BETALINGSMODEL
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="ncnp">
    <div class="container ncnp__inner">

      <!-- LINKS: titel + intro -->
      <div class="ncnp__left">
        <span class="label label--ghost">Payment model</span>
        <h2 class="h2 ncnp__title">
          You pay only<br />when we deliver.<br />
          <span class="ncnp__title-red">No Cure No Pay.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="ncnp__subkop">No fixed salary. No recruitment fees. No long-term contract.</p>
        <p class="ncnp__body">
          No cure no pay is not just a payment model. It is a promise.
          If we do not perform, you pay nothing.<br /><br />
          Our interests are always aligned with yours.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- RECHTS: genummerde stappen -->
      <div class="ncnp__right">
        <p class="ncnp__steps-label">How the model works</p>

        <div class="ncnp__steps">

          <div class="ncnp__step">
            <span class="ncnp__num">01</span>
            <div class="ncnp__step-body">
              <h3 class="ncnp__step-title">Appointment setter</h3>
              <p class="ncnp__step-text">You pay per qualified appointment booked on your calendar. Only leads with genuine buying intent get through. No appointment, no cost.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="ncnp__step">
            <span class="ncnp__num">02</span>
            <div class="ncnp__step-body">
              <h3 class="ncnp__step-title">Closer</h3>
              <p class="ncnp__step-text">You pay only when a deal is actually closed. The closer runs the conversation, uncovers needs, and closes. No result, no cost.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="ncnp__step">
            <span class="ncnp__num">03</span>
            <div class="ncnp__step-body">
              <h3 class="ncnp__step-title">Combination</h3>
              <p class="ncnp__step-text">Full sales outsourcing where ClosersMatch manages the entire journey. From first contact and qualification to closing the deal. One system, one owner.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <div class="ncnp__cta-wrap">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn--red btn--lg" data-meeting-modal-choice>Book your free intake now →</button>
          <p class="ncnp__cta-note">no obligations</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ================================================
       SOCIAL PROOF STRIP
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="stats-strip">
    <div class="container stats-strip__inner">
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat__number">87+</span>
        <span class="stat__label">Certified Closers</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat__number">€2.4M+</span>
        <span class="stat__label">Revenue Generated</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat__number">40+</span>
        <span class="stat__label">Active Business Partners</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat__number">68%</span>
        <span class="stat__label">Average Conversion Uplift</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ================================================
       VOOR CLOSERS & SETTERS
  ================================================ -->
  <section class="voor-closers">
    <div class="container voor-closers__inner">

      <!-- LINKS: alle tekst -->
      <div class="voor-closers__content">
        <span class="label label--ghost">For closers &amp; appointment setters</span>
        <h2 class="h2 voor-closers__title">Companies are ready.<br />You close.</h2>
        <p class="voor-closers__body">
          At ClosersMatch you do not search for assignments. You get matched to companies with warm leads ready to be closed. You focus on closing. We handle the rest.
        </p>

        <!-- Voordelen -->
        <div class="voor-closers__voordelen">

          <div class="voor-closers__voordeel">
            <div class="voor-closers__voordeel-icon">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M4 10l4 4 8-8" stroke="#DD342E" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="voor-closers__voordeel-title">Assignments that fit you</h3>
              <p class="voor-closers__voordeel-text">Matched by industry, sales style, and deal size. No cold outreach, no uncertain months. You are connected to companies where your approach works, and where warm leads are already waiting.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="voor-closers__voordeel">
            <div class="voor-closers__voordeel-icon">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M4 10l4 4 8-8" stroke="#DD342E" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="voor-closers__voordeel-title">Become genuinely great at sales</h3>
              <p class="voor-closers__voordeel-text">CM Certified training is not a certificate for the wall. You learn how to steer every conversation, handle objections, and close the deal, including the tough ones. Intensive role-play, real scenarios, direct feedback. After training you close more. And earn more.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="voor-closers__voordeel">
            <div class="voor-closers__voordeel-icon">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M4 10l4 4 8-8" stroke="#DD342E" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="voor-closers__voordeel-title">Not much sales experience yet?</h3>
              <p class="voor-closers__voordeel-text">Start as an appointment setter. You learn how to qualify leads, open conversations, and keep prospects warm. Real hands-on experience with real companies, every day. When you are ready, the step up to closer is a natural next move. Not required. But possible.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- Statement -->
        <p class="voor-closers__statement">Two roles. One ecosystem. You choose where you start.</p>

        <!-- CTAs -->
        <div class="voor-closers__actions">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn--red btn--lg" data-meeting-modal-person="talent">Apply as a closer →</button>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn--outline-white" data-meeting-modal-person="talent">Start as an appointment setter →</button>
        </div>
      </div>

